                            </p>
                            <p>Our ThunderPlast Ready Dry Mix is manufactured in most Techy – cutting edge machinery. Which is fully Automatic.</p>
                            <h4 class="pd-30">Automatic Dry Mix Plant</h4>
                            <ul>
                                <li>
                                    <p>Fully automatic dry mix plant mainly suitable for the capacity of more than 30 tons per day. The automatic dry mix mortar plant has a simple design, small footprint, small investment, quick effect, continuous production, and high output. The double-shaft paddle mixer does not destroy the original state of the material, ensuring that the coefficient of the dry powder is not reduced due to the shape damage of the heat-insulating material, ensuring the quality of the product. Suitable for medium and small-scale manufacturers, equipped with an automatic packaging system, one-button control of all equipment.</p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p>Fully automatic dry mix plant consists of the storage bin, double shaft paddle mixer, bucket elevator, pre-mix hopper, additive hopper, end product hopper, packing machine, indoor bucket elevator, pulse dust collector, automatic batching machine, steel frame, etc. The storage bin is used to storage raw material, such as : cement, fly ash, sand and other, material.</p>
